Table of document clusters

df = merge(S,art_parg, by="paragraph_num") %>%
           group_by(cluster) %>%
           unnest_tokens(input = paragraph_text, output = word)  %>%
           ungroup() %>%
           anti_join(stop_words) %>%
           filter(!str_detect(word, "\\d"))%>%
           filter(nchar(word)>2)  %>%
           mutate(word_lemma = textstem::lemmatize_words(word)) %>%
           mutate(word_low= tolower(word_lemma)) %>%
           select(-word, -word_lemma) %>%
           set_names('paragraph_num','cluster','text_id','NCHAR','word') %>%
           count(cluster,word) %>%
           bind_tf_idf(word, cluster, n) %>%
           arrange(desc(tf_idf))
       quant = quantile(df$tf_idf)
       df = df %>% 
           filter(tf_idf >= quant[1])%>% 
           cast_dtm(document=cluster, term=word, value=n)
       df = as.data.frame(as.matrix(df))
       
        tot_withinss <- map_dbl(2:(nrow(df)-1),  function(k){
                                model <- kmeans(x = df, centers = k)
                                model$tot.withinss
                                })
        elbow_df <- data.frame(
                               k = 2:(nrow(df)-1),
                               tot_withinss = tot_withinss
                               ) %>% 
            dplyr::mutate(diff = c(NA, rev(diff(rev(tot_withinss))))) 
        elbow_df <- elbow_df %>% filter(diff== max(na.rm = TRUE, elbow_df$diff)) %>%
            select(k) %>%
            as.numeric()
            model_km <- kmeans(x = df, centers = elbow_df+1)
       #model_km <- kmeans(x = df, centers = 5)
       df$Segment = row.names(df)
       df <- mutate(df, cluster = paste("Clus", model_km$cluster, sep = '-')) %>% 
           select(Segment, cluster) 
       
       
       DF = merge(S, df, by.x = "cluster", by.y = "Segment")
       DF = merge(DF, art_parg[,1:2]) %>%
           set_names('paragraph_num', 'segment','document_cluster','text_id')%>%
           select(text_id, everything())
       table(DF$text_id, DF$document_cluster)

df_documents = merge(S,art_parg, by="paragraph_num") %>%
           group_by(cluster) %>%
           unnest_tokens(input = paragraph_text, output = word)  %>%
           ungroup() %>%
           anti_join(stop_words) %>%
           filter(!str_detect(word, "\\d"))%>%
           filter(nchar(word)>2)  %>%
           mutate(word_lemma = textstem::lemmatize_words(word)) %>%
           mutate(word_low= tolower(word_lemma)) %>%
           select(text_id, word_low) %>%
           set_names('text_id','word') %>%
           count(text_id,word) %>%
           filter(nchar(word)>2)

for (k in unique(df_documents$text_id)) {
    d <- df_documents %>% filter(text_id == k)
    print(paste(news$Title[k], 'is about',sep = ''))
    wordcloud(words = d$word, freq = d$n, min.freq = 1,
          max.words=40, random.order=FALSE, rot.per=0.35, 
          colors=brewer.pal(8, "Dark2"))
}
